%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Registry as OCI Registry
    participant API as API Server
    participant Runner as Bare Metal Runner

    User->>User: docker build --tag image:tag
    User->>Registry: docker push image:tag
    User->>API: bencher run --image image:tag
    API->>API: Create pending Job
    API->>API: Create Report linked to Job
    Runner->>API: Poll for Jobs matching Specs
    API-->>Runner: Assign Job
    Runner->>Registry: Pull Image
    Registry-->>Runner: Image layers
    Runner->>Runner: Unpack Image
    Runner->>Runner: Run benchmark command
    Runner->>API: Submit benchmark results
    API->>API: Parse via benchmark harness adapter
    API->>API: Attach results to Report
    User->>API: Poll for Job completion
    API-->>User: Completed Report
